description:
With this DLC you will unlock:

- painting selected parts of the nail with a brush 
- spider accessory
- skull accessory
- eyeballs accessory
- scary face accessory
- bats stencil
- spider's web stencil
- skull stencil
- bat stencil
- scary face stencil 
- scary face stencil second version 

Create your amazing designs with a nail polish brush and use your new Halloween-themed accessories or stencils!
name: Acrylic Nails!: Spooky Painting
